  <acronym>APTE</acronym>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of the Concentrate of Autologous Rich Plasma in Growth Factors in the Treatment of the Thin Endometrium in Patients Undergoing Transfer of Cryo-preserved Embryos: Clinical Trial II.</official_title>
