  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluate the percentaje of women with thin endometrium who achieve an endometrial
      thickness equal to or greater than 7 mm after administration of PRGF (plasma rich in growth
      factors)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
